e.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.currentRoute and isShellAtTop remain `@State` fields that re-render the shell host immediately when route or top state changes.\",\"Target review: entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/app_router.cj::ShellRouteState.setTopState and showBottomShell preserve the combined route-plus-top-state visibility rule across shell commands.\",\"Test verification: 2026-06-25 manual reproduction of `cjpm test --target aarch64-linux-ohos` in D:/workspace/Foodike/Foodike-Harmony/entry passed with shellRouteStatePreservesTopFlagAcrossCommands and bottomShellOnlyShowsOnTopLevelHomeAndHistoryRoutes.\"],\"targetEndpoints\":[\"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.currentRoute\",\"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.isShellAtTop\",\"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.applyShellState\",\"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/app_router.cj::ShellRouteState.setTopState\",\"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/app_router.cj::ShellRouteState.showBottomShell\",\"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/app_router.cj::showsBottomShell\"],\"tests\":[\"entry/src/test/cangjie/phase02_startup_navigation_test.cj::Phase02StartupNavigationTest.bottomShellOnlyShowsOnTopLevelHomeAndHistoryRoutes\",\"entry/src/test/cangjie/phase02_startup_navigation_test.cj::Phase02StartupNavigationTest.shellRouteStatePreservesTopFlagAcrossCommands\"],\"notes\":\"The earlier simplification was that route commands reset shell-top state. The extracted ShellRouteState now preserves top-state across duplicate-safe tab/cart commands, matching the source observable shell behavior for this phase.\"}}]}\n\n","files":[{"filePath":"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\agent-inputs\\phase02_presentation_util_patch.json","relativePath":"translation-inputs/agent-inputs/phase02_presentation_util_patch.json","type"